<p>
<p>You can analyze a glass of water and you're left with a lot of chemical  components, but nothing you can drink.
<p>
<p>J. B. S. HALDANE
<p>
<p>You think too much, that is your trouble. Clever people and grocers,  they weigh everything.
<p>
<p>ZORBA THE GREEK
