<LI><A HREF="tuesday.html">Daily report Tuesday 8 October 1996</A> (BASF)
<LI><A HREF="wednesday.html">Daily report Wednesday 9 October 1996</A> (University of Stuttgart)
<LI><A HREF="thursday.html">Daily report Thursday 10 October 1996</A> (Council of Europe, Doctorate of honour)
<LI><A HREF="friday.html">Daily report Friday 11 October 1996</A> (Solvay, ENSIC)
<LI><A HREF="saterday.html">Daily report Saterday 12 October 1996</A> (Remouchamps)
<LI><A HREF="dsm.html">Daily report Thusrday 31 October and Friday 1 November 1996</A> (DSM)
</UL>
</UL>

