<HTML>
<HEAD>
   <TITLE>General Information about the OSPT</TITLE>
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.0Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../back/tile2.gif">

<P><A NAME="top"></A></P>

<TABLE>
<TR>
<TD><A HREF="../index.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_ospt.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=44></A><BR>
<A HREF="../agenda/index.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_agenda.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=22></A><A HREF="../news/index.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_news.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=22></A><BR>
<A HREF="../minipost/index.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_phd.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=22></A><A HREF="../2efase/index.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_2efase.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=22></A><BR>
<A HREF="index.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_info.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=22></A><A HREF="../help.html"><IMG SRC="../pic/button/b_help.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=22 WIDTH=22></A><BR>
</TD>

<TD>
<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>General Information about the OSPT</H2>
</TD>

<TD><MAP NAME="logo.map"><AREA SHAPE="RECT" COORDS="38,21,108,51" HREF="../index.html"></MAP><IMG USEMAP="#logo.map" SRC="../pic/logo/adetgw__.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=85 WIDTH=149>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

<P>
<HR><A NAME="intro"></A><B>Introduction:</B> <A HREF="#part"><IMG SRC="../pic/a_down.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=20></A><A HREF="#top"><IMG SRC="../pic/a_up.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=20></A><BR>
Within the OSPT <A HREF="#part">six universities</A> which are active in
the area of Process Technology are collaborating; total 9 faculties, involving
25 research groups with 39 (full-time and part-time) professors and about
250 lectures, post-docs, PhD students and research associates.</P>

<P> The OSPT aims at: </P>

<UL>
<LI>Strengthening of the Process Technology in the Netherlands </LI>

<LI>Strengthening of the research through stimulation and coordination
of research programs </LI>

<LI>Stimulation of top research </LI>

<LI>Coordination of education and initiation of advanced graduate courses
on Process Technology for PhD-students, designers and interested professionals
from industry </LI>

<LI>Promoting international contacts by inviting visiting teachers and
top researchers and creating networks for collaboration </LI>

<LI>Providing an interface between the process industry and the universities
through direct contacts and an <A HREF="#iab">industrial advisory board</A>
</LI>

<LI>Acquisition of funds for R&amp;D and education programs of the school
</LI>
</UL>

Important axes of research are: physical transport phenomena, chemical reaction engineering, separation technology, process integration/development and the input of these disciplines in multi-disciplinary projects.<BR>
The basic ideas behind the research programs are discussed in different strategic documents of the school, a.o. in the "Research Perspectives" (see: R. Krishna, J.A. Wesselingh and W.P.M. van Swaaij; Chemical Engineering Research in the Netherlands, <B>1992</B>, <I>Trans. J. Chem. E.</I>, vol. 70, part A, 166-172).

<P><A NAME="part"></A><B>Participants:</B> <A HREF="#secr"><IMG SRC="../pic/a_down.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=20></A><A HREF="#intro"><IMG SRC="../pic/a_up.gif" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=20></A>
</P>

<UL TYPE=square>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.uva.nl/uva/english/">University of Amsterdam</A>
(UVA) </LI>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.chem.uva.nl/">Faculty of Chemistry</A> </LI>
</UL>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.tudelft.nl/">Delft University of Technology</A>
(TUD) </LI>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.stm.tudelft.nl/">Faculty of Chemical Technology
and Materials Science</A> </LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.tn.tudelft.nl/">Faculty of Applied Physics</A>
</LI>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.wbmt.tudelft.nl/index_e.htm">Faculty of Mechanical
Engineering and Marine Technology</A> </LI>
</UL>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.tue.nl/english/">Technical University of Eindhoven</A>
(TUE) </LI>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.chem.tue.nl/">Faculty of Chemical Technology</A>
</LI>
</UL>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.rug.nl/rug/lijstuk.html">State University of Groningen</A>
(RUG) </LI>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.fwn.rug.nl/engels.html">Faculty of Mathematics
and Physical Sciences</A> </LI>
</UL>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.utwente.nl/uthomuk.htm">University of Twente</A>
(UT) </LI>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ct.utwente.nl/">Faculty of Chemical Technology</A>
