<HEAD><TITLE>Phd-projects Amsterdam 1996</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../../back/tile2.gif">

<H2>Chemical Reaction Engineering<HR></H2>

<TT><PRE>
University of Amsterdam
Department of Chemical Engineering
Nieuwe Achtergracht 166
NL 1018 WV Amsterdam

telephone: +31 (0)20 525 7007
fax:       +31 (0)20 525 5604
e-mail:    <A HREF="mailto:krishna@chemeng.chem.uva.nl">krishna@chemeng.chem.uva.nl</A>
internet:  <A HREF="http://ctwww.chem.uva.nl/cr/">http://ctwww.chem.uva.nl/cr/</A>
</PRE></TT>

<H6><CENTER><HR>&copy; OSPT - <A HREF="mailto:OSPT@ct.utwente.nl"> OSPT@ct.utwente.nl</A> - last modification 01/11/96</CENTER></H6>

</BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT25-B28-119</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000114-B046-380</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost96/uva/krishna.html 130.89.50.60 19970216174023 text/html 19736
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 17:33:45 GMT
