<TITLE>Least squares image reconstruction for electrical capacitance tomography (ECT)
</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="../../back/tile2.gif">

<TABLE><TR><TD>
<H2>Least squares image reconstruction for electrical capacitance tomography (ECT)</H2>
PhD-student: Dipl.-Ing. Frank T. K&uuml;hn (1)hone: 015-786329)<BR>
Sponsors: I.M. Burgerscentrum<BR>
Cooperation: joint project of the research groulps of Van den Bleek, Scarlett and Van den Akker<BR>
</TD><TD> </TD></TR></TABLE>

<HR SIZE=0>

