<DOCNO>WT25-B28-193</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000115-B003-85</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost96/tud/102.html 130.89.50.60 19970216175557 text/html 2676
