http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost96/tud/ospt96jf.html 130.89.50.60 19970216180026 text/html 3571
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 17:53:52 GMT
