<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT25-B28-236</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000115-B017-78</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost96/tud/pv.html 130.89.50.60 19970216180505 text/html 2720
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 17:58:31 GMT
