<H2>Chemical Reactor Engineering and Process Development<HR></H2>

<TT><PRE>
Technical University of Eindhoven
Faculty of Chemical Technology
P.O. Box 513
NL 5600 MB Eindhoven

telephone: +31 (0)40 247 4111/2241
fax:       +31 (0)40 244 6104
</PRE></TT>

<HR>

EINDHOVEN UNIVERSITY OF TECHNOLOGY<BR>
DEPARTMENT OF CHEMICAL PROCESS TECHNOLOGY<BR>
RESEARCH GROUP "CHEMICAL REACTOR ENGINEERING AND PROCESS DEVELOPMENT"<BR>
P.O. Box 513, 5600 MB Eindhoven. Phone: 040.247.4111/247.2241, Fax: 040.244.6104.<BR>
<P>
Research is carried out in the field of Chemical Reaction Engineering, especially focussed on gas-solid
and liquid-solid dispersions. The main subjects are fluidisation, non-steady state processing,
hydrodynamics of low and high viscosity liquids, especially in stirred tanks, and polymer reaction
engineering. Pilot scale equipment is available for part of the experimental work.<P>

