<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000115-B020-273</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost96/ut/249.html 130.89.50.60 19970216181853 text/html 2903
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 18:12:20 GMT
