<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000115-B021-136</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost96/ut/roffel.html 130.89.50.60 19970216182115 text/html 4009
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 18:14:41 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.3
